      "writtenOn": "2026-01-28T23:15:32Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Yes, if a group has the lint targets and they are behind conditionals this can happen. For example in `build_webgui.gn` in Chromium we have targets that point to this group:\n```\n  group(\"lint\") {\n    deps \u003d []\n    if (enable_type_aware_eslint_checks) {\n      deps +\u003d [ \":lint_ts\" ]\n    }\n\n    if (defined(invoker.css_files)) {\n      deps +\u003d [ \":lint_css\" ]\n    }\n  }\n```",
